19:33.760 --> 19:34.830
-Hello.
-These are my families.

19:35.240 --> 19:35.750
Hello, aunt.

19:36.050 --> 19:37.010
- Hello.
- Aunt looks so young.

19:37.240 --> 19:37.790
If you didn't tell me,

19:37.810 --> 19:39.090
I'd think she’s your sister.

19:41.830 --> 19:42.450
What a coincidence.

19:45.420 --> 19:46.540
Dad, these are the seniors

19:46.570 --> 19:47.650
of my laboratory.

19:47.850 --> 19:49.130
This is Xiao Yuhe.

19:49.160 --> 19:50.480
This is Liu Dongmao.

19:50.760 --> 19:51.260
Hello, uncle.

19:51.900 --> 19:53.670
The demands on our laboratory are high.

19:53.760 --> 19:54.440
I certainly wouldn't be able to stay

19:54.440 --> 19:55.080
without them

19:55.100 --> 19:55.990
taking care of me.

19:56.210 --> 19:57.320
Not at all.

19:57.690 --> 19:58.560
Let me invite you to lunch.

19:58.680 --> 19:59.520
No need, uncle.

19:59.560 --> 20:00.350
That table is almost cleared.

20:00.410 --> 20:00.920
Maybe next time.

20:01.000 --> 20:01.620
Bye, uncle.

20:01.660 --> 20:02.330
Bye, uncle.

20:02.980 --> 20:03.660
Here.

20:04.050 --> 20:05.090
Chengcheng's favorite dish,

20:05.110 --> 20:06.890
beef with cilantro.

20:15.580 --> 20:16.030
Chengcheng.

20:17.600 --> 20:18.820
I remember you don't eat cilantro.

20:20.400 --> 20:20.950
Right.

20:21.350 --> 20:23.210
It is your younger brother
who likes cilantro best.

20:24.240 --> 20:25.150
Look at me.

20:29.940 --> 20:30.870
Come on.

20:31.150 --> 20:32.360
Here, chopsticks.

20:35.390 --> 20:35.950
Chengcheng.

20:36.650 --> 20:37.440
Sorry.

20:37.590 --> 20:38.310
Nothing.

20:41.500 --> 20:42.510
Let’s eat.

20:43.220 --> 20:43.700
So delicious.

20:44.370 --> 20:45.650
The meat looks good.

20:48.370 --> 20:48.730
Here.

20:49.360 --> 20:49.880
Thank you.

20:51.200 --> 20:51.550
Dongmao.

20:52.340 --> 20:52.870
Your plate.

21:01.180 --> 21:01.750
[Xiao Junlan]

21:15.040 --> 21:15.920
Hello, more seasoning.

21:24.360 --> 21:24.920
Your seasoning, please.

21:24.920 --> 21:25.260
Thank you.

21:25.570 --> 21:26.160
You are welcome.

21:29.710 --> 21:30.910
In the past few years,

21:31.010 --> 21:32.270
Dr. Zhang from the School of Computer Science

21:32.300 --> 21:33.610
and the three of us came here together during the Mid-Autumn Festival.

21:33.990 --> 21:34.420
Look.

21:34.730 --> 21:36.120
Since he had a girlfriend,

21:36.120 --> 21:36.970
let alone the Mid-Autumn Festival,

21:37.010 --> 21:38.240
we haven't seen him in any festival.

21:39.120 --> 21:39.710
By the way, Yuhe.

21:40.750 --> 21:41.780
Aren’t you a local?

21:41.890 --> 21:42.970
Why do you seldom

21:43.110 --> 21:43.880
go home?

21:43.950 --> 21:44.760
It’s Mid-Autumn Festival today.

21:50.040 --> 21:50.610
My parents separated

21:50.630 --> 21:51.830
when I was a kid.

21:53.250 --> 21:54.370
I don't like festivals,

21:55.000 --> 21:55.720
so I don't often come back.

22:00.560 --> 22:01.250
I understand.

22:01.940 --> 22:03.970
But it’s after all the Mid-Autumn Festival,

22:04.280 --> 22:06.620
you have to be with your family,

22:06.640 --> 22:07.090
right?

22:08.000 --> 22:09.140
And you can talk everything

22:10.050 --> 22:11.390
with your family.

22:12.480 --> 22:12.880
Right.

22:13.490 --> 22:14.550
How about we have something to drink?

22:14.800 --> 22:15.200
Sure.

22:15.490 --> 22:16.820
To celebrate the festival.

22:17.120 --> 22:17.530
What do you want?

22:18.880 --> 22:19.770
Mineral water.

22:21.000 --> 22:21.900
The same to me.

22:23.190 --> 22:23.670
Waiter.

22:24.030 --> 22:25.160
Two mineral water

22:25.210 --> 22:26.680
and one iced Coke.

22:38.050 --> 22:40.130
A signature durian mango flavour.

22:40.560 --> 22:41.000
Okay.

22:41.070 --> 22:42.560
And a Mango Sago.

22:42.880 --> 22:43.230
Okay.

22:43.670 --> 22:44.140
What do you want?

22:46.080 --> 22:48.220
Your brother is cute, isn’t he?

22:50.030 --> 22:51.130
How are you at school?

22:52.830 --> 22:53.460
Good.

22:54.120 --> 22:54.730
Are you short of money?

22:55.040 --> 22:55.900
Not at all.

22:56.200 --> 22:56.720
By the way,

22:57.120 --> 22:58.680
are you graduating from college next year?

23:03.370 --> 23:05.050
I'm just a sophomore this year, dad.

23:07.090 --> 23:08.230
What's wrong with me today?

23:15.120 --> 23:17.170
Take it to buy something you like.

23:27.230 --> 23:28.640
Now no one gives cash.

23:29.030 --> 23:30.290
All transfers are made online.

23:33.990 --> 23:34.850
Your aunt

23:36.740 --> 23:38.580
will check my transfer records.

23:40.830 --> 23:41.950
I'm sorry for you.

23:56.960 --> 23:57.440
Grandpa Liu.

23:59.110 --> 23:59.840
Yuhe is back.

24:02.320 --> 24:02.750
Grandpa Huang.

24:02.770 --> 24:04.130
Yuhe, long time no see.

24:05.210 --> 24:05.770
Go ahead.

24:06.290 --> 24:06.890
Sure.

24:07.570 --> 24:08.320
Let’s continue.

24:09.640 --> 24:10.480
Look at you.

24:10.570 --> 24:11.100
Granny Guan.

24:11.130 --> 24:11.950
Yuhe is back.

24:12.170 --> 24:13.870
You are getting more and more handsome.

24:14.110 --> 24:15.150
You finally learned it,

24:15.360 --> 24:16.400
but why did you forget everything

24:16.420 --> 24:17.380
in the exam today?

24:18.970 --> 24:19.890
Yuhe is back.

24:19.920 --> 24:20.270
Aunt.

24:21.170 --> 24:21.840
Can't you

24:21.840 --> 24:23.320
learn more from Yuhe?

24:23.600 --> 24:24.860
When Yuhe was young,

24:25.200 --> 24:26.630
his mother never worried about him.

24:29.600 --> 24:29.910
It’s okay.

24:30.890 --> 24:32.240
Step by step.

25:19.230 --> 25:20.400
Mom, I’m back.

25:20.990 --> 25:21.580
You are back.

25:23.140 --> 25:24.120
The meal is almost ready.

25:24.240 --> 25:25.080
I am preparing a soup.

25:25.800 --> 25:26.760
I will go back to my room.

27:00.890 --> 27:03.060
I made chicken soup for you.

27:07.560 --> 27:09.180
I didn't put any salt in it.

27:09.200 --> 27:10.090
But I think

27:10.650 --> 27:12.240
it is a bit fishy without salt.

27:14.580 --> 27:15.570
Let me add some soup.

27:15.860 --> 27:17.210
I don't like chicken soup with salt.

27:17.920 --> 27:19.120
I know.

27:19.400 --> 27:20.570
But it’s fishy

27:21.320 --> 27:22.370
without salt.

27:22.800 --> 27:23.420
Add some.

27:53.740 --> 27:54.300
Try this.

28:22.930 --> 28:25.250
Mom, where is

28:25.290 --> 28:26.180
our family photo?

28:33.880 --> 28:34.810
I felt that

28:36.030 --> 28:37.010
some of the furnishings in our house

28:39.960 --> 28:40.580
were quite old,

28:41.600 --> 28:43.050
and they would be a nuisance,

28:43.360 --> 28:44.330
so I

28:44.620 --> 28:45.010
threw them all away.

28:48.820 --> 28:49.750
Indeed.

28:52.610 --> 28:53.570
But I don't feel like

28:54.610 --> 28:55.890
a photo is a nuisance.

28:56.560 --> 28:57.060
And

28:58.490 --> 28:59.990
you shouldn't deal with my items

29:00.280 --> 29:01.470
without my permission.

29:15.020 --> 29:17.080
Eat first.

29:17.450 --> 29:18.420
Let’s talk after the meal.

29:44.360 --> 29:45.100
I’ve had enough, mom.

29:45.430 --> 29:45.800
Tell me

29:47.260 --> 29:47.810
where did you throw it.

29:57.400 --> 29:58.270
What do you mean?

30:01.320 --> 30:02.680
Are you trying to get it back?

30:08.880 --> 30:10.110
You care so much about your dad,

30:13.730 --> 30:16.530
but he left you at home

30:16.720 --> 30:17.920
and went abroad by himself.

30:31.880 --> 30:32.990
Think about it.

30:35.050 --> 30:36.210
I have been busy

30:36.260 --> 30:37.210
working for you

30:37.240 --> 30:38.040
since you were a child,

30:38.120 --> 30:39.330
raising you up.

30:40.640 --> 30:41.650
Have you

30:41.650 --> 30:42.560
considered my feelings

30:43.130 --> 30:43.680
during the years

30:45.270 --> 30:45.620
when that photo

30:48.070 --> 30:49.480
was kept at home?

31:00.270 --> 31:01.350
I have something to do in the lab.

31:02.340 --> 31:03.040
I’m leaving.

31:12.280 --> 31:14.550
Mom, what you threw away

31:14.580 --> 31:16.060
was a photo of our family,

31:17.430 --> 31:18.710
not just that of my dad.

32:00.480 --> 32:00.980
Chengcheng.

32:02.040 --> 32:02.810
Don’t you need me to send you back?

32:03.360 --> 32:04.370
No need, dad.

32:04.520 --> 32:05.900
It is very convenient to take a taxi here,

32:05.920 --> 32:07.200
and it is not far from the school.

32:07.610 --> 32:08.240
You can get on the expressway

32:08.240 --> 32:08.880
directly from here.

32:08.900 --> 32:09.470
Very convenient.

32:11.540 --> 32:12.070
I see.

32:21.550 --> 32:22.580
Take it, Chengcheng.

32:22.640 --> 32:23.690
Let’s not be like this.

32:25.130 --> 32:26.890
I’m really not short of money.

32:27.710 --> 32:28.910
Look, aunt bought me

32:28.930 --> 32:30.040
a lot of things already.

32:30.240 --> 32:31.410
That's enough for me.

32:32.080 --> 32:32.730
You don't have to be so embarrassed

32:32.760 --> 32:33.440
because of me.

32:36.430 --> 32:37.080
Your brother is coming.

32:43.720 --> 32:44.080
Here you are.

32:44.750 --> 32:45.320
Chengcheng.

32:45.900 --> 32:47.220
You should have a few days left

32:47.250 --> 32:48.340
on your vacation.

32:48.450 --> 32:49.690
Don't you want to hang out with us?

32:49.880 --> 32:50.360
It's boring

32:50.390 --> 32:51.210
to be alone in school.

32:51.680 --> 32:52.900
I’m not going, aunt.

32:53.680 --> 32:54.290
I...

32:56.250 --> 32:57.130
Anything in school?

32:57.530 --> 32:58.260
I haven’t

32:58.400 --> 32:59.640
finished my homework.

33:00.170 --> 33:01.370
So I want to catch up

33:01.390 --> 33:02.420
during the holidays.

33:02.960 --> 33:03.920
Alright.

33:04.160 --> 33:04.980
That’s fine.

33:05.370 --> 33:06.960
Come home next time you have a holiday.

33:06.990 --> 33:08.030
I'll cook something delicious for you.

33:08.110 --> 33:08.530
Okay.

33:09.090 --> 33:09.920
Say goodbye to your sister.

33:10.300 --> 33:11.010
Bye.

33:11.810 --> 33:12.850
Get in the car.

33:14.130 --> 33:15.260
Keep in touch.

34:27.270 --> 34:27.949
Take a seat.

34:28.850 --> 34:30.639
The bus is dangling and dangerous.

34:31.409 --> 34:32.449
You will fall down.

34:33.230 --> 34:34.210
-No.
-Stand firm.

34:39.159 --> 34:40.260
Take a seat.

34:40.710 --> 34:41.420
So naughty.

34:43.239 --> 34:44.790
I want to eat McDonald's tonight.

34:45.540 --> 34:46.820
McDonald's again?

34:47.000 --> 34:48.570
You are so fat!

34:48.590 --> 34:50.210
Look at you.

34:50.989 --> 34:51.880
Am I?

34:52.020 --> 34:53.060
No?

34:53.090 --> 34:54.650
What a fatty.

34:56.090 --> 34:57.280
You…Listen.

34:57.960 --> 35:00.500
If you get ninety-five points in the English test,

34:59.450 --> 35:04.020
[Dad]

35:01.000 --> 35:03.000
I will take you to McDonald's.

35:03.030 --> 35:04.460
Okay, deal.

35:04.590 --> 35:06.240
Deal.

35:06.830 --> 35:07.660
Pinky promise.

35:10.120 --> 35:11.010
You know

35:11.010 --> 35:11.640
your mom well.

35:12.160 --> 35:13.030
I really worry about

35:14.120 --> 35:15.050
you living with her.

35:16.360 --> 35:17.200
I have already processed your documents

35:17.200 --> 35:18.190
for going abroad.

35:18.670 --> 35:19.390
Think about it.

35:20.090 --> 35:21.900
How about going abroad with me?

35:24.590 --> 35:25.870
I have decided to stay here.

35:29.950 --> 35:30.370
Alright.

35:31.200 --> 35:32.040
You have grown up.

35:32.410 --> 35:33.450
I understand

35:34.080 --> 35:34.660
you have your own ideas.

35:35.610 --> 35:36.880
If you encounter any difficulties in the future,

35:38.080 --> 35:39.050
let me know anytime,

35:39.300 --> 35:40.570
and I will make it back to see you.

35:41.920 --> 35:43.500
Dad, don't worry about that.

35:44.340 --> 35:45.340
I’ve made

35:45.360 --> 35:46.480
a good friend at school.

35:47.060 --> 35:48.160
Her name is Su Chengcheng.

35:49.610 --> 35:50.470
She is very nice to me.

35:50.960 --> 35:52.360
Whenever I meet difficulties,

35:52.360 --> 35:53.210
she will help me.

35:53.830 --> 35:54.460
Really?

35:55.030 --> 35:55.880
You kid!

35:56.520 --> 35:57.080
Are you finally willing

35:57.080 --> 35:57.930
to be friends with your classmates?

35:59.610 --> 36:01.130
But you have to study hard.

36:03.560 --> 36:04.240
I am leaving.

36:05.120 --> 36:05.710
I bought you

36:05.730 --> 36:06.610
a new mobile phone.

36:07.230 --> 36:08.030
Remember to call me.

36:08.780 --> 36:09.140
Okay.

36:56.120 --> 36:57.790
Chengcheng doesn't like cilantro.

36:58.400 --> 36:59.680
Dad will help you pick up

36:59.710 --> 37:00.840
all the cilantro,

37:01.050 --> 37:01.570
okay?

37:01.730 --> 37:02.120
Okay!

37:09.840 --> 37:11.480
Smile.

37:22.120 --> 37:22.790
What are you doing?

37:24.000 --> 37:24.480
Hold on.

37:24.500 --> 37:25.190
I'm going to see Chengcheng.

37:25.320 --> 37:27.250
It’s late. Don’t go in.

37:27.280 --> 37:28.130
Look at you.

37:28.160 --> 37:29.830
Why are you so drunk every day?

37:29.970 --> 37:30.740
Just take a look.

37:31.630 --> 37:32.900
What are you doing, Su Zhiqiang?

37:33.570 --> 37:34.020
Chengcheng.

37:34.790 --> 37:35.910
My good girl.

37:36.170 --> 37:37.130
She looks so much like me.

37:37.330 --> 37:38.930
My baby!

37:38.960 --> 37:39.530
Enough.

37:39.570 --> 37:40.580
Leave.

37:40.610 --> 37:41.280
Get out.

37:41.470 --> 37:43.150
Get out.

37:43.370 --> 37:43.800
No way.

37:44.050 --> 37:44.740
What else do you want?

37:45.310 --> 37:46.640
I’m giving a present to my daughter.

37:48.550 --> 37:49.070
Get out.

37:49.360 --> 37:50.220
Her favorite.

37:50.810 --> 37:52.580
Chengcheng, I love you.

37:52.720 --> 37:53.330
I love you.

37:53.580 --> 37:54.100
Chengcheng.

37:54.230 --> 37:55.450
Enough.

37:56.200 --> 37:57.010
Leave.

37:57.800 --> 37:58.360
Look at you.

37:59.090 --> 37:59.880
Get out.

37:59.960 --> 38:01.170
Chengcheng, I love you.
